<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>The Director of this Office is responsible for overseeing the delivery of our objectives as set out in our <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/scotland-office-business-plan-2012-to-2013">business plan</a>.</p>

<p>In addition to policy teams covering the range of reserved matters the office also has a ministerial private office, press office and a finance and administration section.</p>

<h2 id="joint-management-board">Joint Management Board</h2>

<p>Our Office and the Office of the Advocate General (<abbr title="Office of the Advocate General">OAG</abbr>) for Scotland have a common governance structure and a single Parliamentary vote.</p>

<p>The offices have a Joint Management Board (<abbr title="Joint Management Board">JMB</abbr>) chaired by the Secretary of State for Scotland. Our Director is the Principal Accounting Officer for both offices.</p>

<p>The board meets regularly and considers a wide range of issues, from the overall complement of the offices to the budgeting allocations within the offices.</p>

<p>Read the edited versions of the <abbr title="Joint Management Board">JMB</abbr> minutes:</p>

